I cant put my finger on exactly why (maybe for the same reason that describng music is almost entirely impossible??) but i know that you, on average, make me feel happy, but that average also skims over the bits where u make me feel sad or reflective or bewildered or worried or whtever else we percieve (those feelings arent bad, theyre feelings).
